name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TabJockey - Mute All Tabs with Ease

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Take control of audio tabs with TabJockey - track, mute, and close audio tabs effortlessly!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: TabJockey is a powerful Chrome web extension designed to enhance your browsing experience by giving you complete control over browser tabs with audio. With TabJockey, you can effortlessly track, mute, and close audio tabs, ensuring a seamless and distraction-free browsing experience.
